{"an4.18:0.1":"Anguttara Nikaya 4.18 ","an4.18:0.2":"2. Caravagga ","an4.18:0.3":"Dutiyaagatisutta ","an4.18:1.1":"“Cattarimani, bhikkhave, nagatigamanani. ","an4.18:1.2":"Katamani cattari? ","an4.18:1.3":"Na chandagatim gacchati, na dosagatim gacchati, na mohagatim gacchati, na bhayagatim gacchati—","an4.18:1.4":"Imani kho, bhikkhave, cattari nagatigamananiti. ","an4.18:2.1":"Chanda dosa bhaya moha, ","an4.18:2.2":"yo dhammam nativattati; ","an4.18:2.3":"Apurati tassa yaso, ","an4.18:2.4":"sukkapakkheva candima”ti. ","an4.18:2.5":"Atthamam. "}